## RÈGLE 11 - COMPLIANCE & LEGAL
# Conformité RGPD, ANSSI, WCAG

ALWAYS ensure:
- Personal data processing has legal basis (RGPD Art. 6)
- User consent collected before data collection
- Data retention policies implemented (auto-delete after X days)
- Accessibility WCAG 2.2 AA compliance for frontend
- ANSSI 2026 password policy (12+ chars, complexity, no reuse)

NEVER implement:
- Data collection without explicit user consent
- Permanent data storage without retention policy
- Inaccessible UI elements (missing ARIA labels)
- Weak password policies

## RÈGLE 12 - EMERGENCY ROLLBACK
# Capacité de rollback en cas de détection de faille

ALWAYS maintain:
- Tagged Docker images for each deployment
- Database migration rollback scripts
- Configuration backups before changes
- Incident response documentation

